Package: echosmart-gateway
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-venv, ${misc:Depends}
Description: EchoSmart IoT Gateway for greenhouse monitoring
 The EchoSmart Gateway reads environmental sensors (temperature,
 humidity, CO₂, light, soil moisture) on a Raspberry Pi and sends
 data to the EchoSmart cloud platform via MQTT / HTTP.
 .
 Includes a CLI (echosmart-gateway), a systemd service, and a
 first-boot setup wizard (echosmart-gateway-setup).
